javax.servlet.Filter
@Scope(value=APPLICATION)
@Name(value="org.jboss.seam.web.ajax4jsfFilter")
@Install(precedence=0,
         dependencies="org.jboss.seam.web.ajax4jsfFilterInstantiator")
@BypassInterceptors
@Filter
public class Ajax4jsfFilter
extends AbstractFilter

A Seam filter component wrapper for the Ajax4JSF. This class exists to allow the Ajax4JSF filter to be configured in the web: namespace. The subclass does the actual work.

Author:
Pete Muir
